graph LR
    ODHNotebookController[ODH Notebook Controller]

    %% External Dependencies
    ODHNotebookController -->|creates notebooks| KubeflowController[Kubeflow Notebook<br/>Controller v1<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODHNotebookController -->|HTTPRoute/Gateway CRDs| GatewayAPI[Gateway API<br/>v1.2.1<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODHNotebookController -->|TLS certificates| ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA<br/>Operator 4.19+<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODHNotebookController -->|sidecar proxy| KubeRBACProxy[kube-rbac-proxy<br/>Latest<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODHNotebookController -->|core APIs| Kubernetes[Kubernetes 1.33+<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODHNotebookController -->|OpenShift APIs| OpenShift[OpenShift 4.19+<br/>REQUIRED]
    ODHNotebookController -->|framework| ControllerRuntime[controller-runtime<br/>v0.21.0<br/>REQUIRED]

    %% Internal ODH Dependencies
    ODHNotebookController -->|routes traffic| DataScienceGateway[Data Science Gateway<br/>Gateway API]
    ODHNotebookController -->|watches DSPA CRs| DSPOperator[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Operator<br/>CRD Watch]
    ODHNotebookController -->|enhances CRs from| OdhDashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>Notebook CRD]
    ODHNotebookController -.->|mounts CA bundle| TrustedCA[Trusted CA Bundle<br/>ConfigMap]

    %% Integration Points (reverse)
    OdhDashboard -->|creates CRs| ODHNotebookController
    DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -->|integrates via| ODHNotebookController

    %% External Services
    ODHNotebookController -->|model storage| S3[S3 Storage<br/>AWS/MinIO]
    ODHNotebookController -->|image pulls| ImageRegistry[Image Registry<br/>OCP/External]
    ODHNotebookController -.->|optional proxy| ClusterProxy[OpenShift Proxy<br/>config.openshift.io]

    %% API Server (critical dependency)
    ODHNotebookController -->|all operations| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+]

    %% Styling
    style ODHNotebookController fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px,color:#fff

